<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="languageicon">(in Greek)</span> <cite id="CITEREFStrabo1877" class="citation book cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source">Strabo (1877). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Strab.+11.11.1&amp;fromdoc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0197">"11.11.1"</a>. In Meineke, A. (ed.). <i>Geographica</i> (in Greek). Leipzig: Teubner.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=11.11.1&amp;rft.btitle=Geographica&amp;rft.place=Leipzig&amp;rft.pub=Teubner&amp;rft.date=1877&amp;rft.au=Strabo&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.perseus.tufts.edu%2Fhopper%2Ftext%3Fdoc%3DStrab.%2B11.11.1%26fromdoc%3DPerseus%253Atext%253A1999.01.0197&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMenander+I" class="Z3988"></span><br /><cite id="CITEREFJones1924" class="citation book cs1">Jones, H. L., ed. (1924). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Strab.+11.11.1&amp;fromdoc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0198">"11.11.1"</a>. <i>Strabo, Geography, Book 11, chapter 11, section 1</i>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=11.11.1&amp;rft.btitle=Strabo%2C+Geography%2C+Book+11%2C+chapter+11%2C+section+1&amp;rft.date=1924&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.perseus.tufts.edu%2Fhopper%2Ftext%3Fdoc%3DStrab.%2B11.11.1%26fromdoc%3DPerseus%253Atext%253A1999.01.0198&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMenander+I" class="Z3988"></span> <cite id="CITEREFJones1903" class="citation book cs1">Jones, H. L., ed. (1903). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0239%3Abook%3D11%3Achapter%3D11%3Asection%3D1">"11.11.1"</a>. <i>Strabo, Geography, BOOK XI., CHAPTER XI., section 1</i>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=11.11.1&amp;rft.btitle=Strabo%2C+Geography%2C+BOOK+XI.%2C+CHAPTER+XI.%2C+section+1&amp;rft.date=1903&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.perseus.tufts.edu%2Fhopper%2Ftext%3Fdoc%3DPerseus%253Atext%253A1999.01.0239%253Abook%253D11%253Achapter%253D11%253Asection%253D1&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMenander+I" class="Z3988"></span> At the Perseus Project.</span>
