<td style="width: 40%; text-align: center;" rowspan="2"><b> <a href="/wiki/Indo-Greek" class="mw-redirect" title="Indo-Greek">Indo-Greek ruler</a> <br /> (in <a href="/wiki/Paropamisadae" title="Paropamisadae">Paropamisadae</a>, <a href="/wiki/Arachosia" title="Arachosia">Arachosia</a>, <a href="/wiki/Gandhara" title="Gandhara">Gandhara</a>, <a href="/wiki/Punjab_(Pakistan)" class="mw-redirect" title="Punjab (Pakistan)">Punjab</a>) </b><br />155/150 – 130 BC
</td>
<td style="width: 30%; text-align: center;" rowspan="1">Succeeded&#160;by<div style="font-weight: bold"><a href="/wiki/Zoilos_I" class="mw-redirect" title="Zoilos I">Zoilos I</a><br />(in <a href="/wiki/Paropamisadae" title="Paropamisadae">Paropamisadae</a>, <a href="/wiki/Arachosia" title="Arachosia">Arachosia</a>)</div>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 30%; text-align: center;" rowspan="1">Succeeded&#160;by<div style="font-weight: bold"><a href="/wiki/Agathokleia" class="mw-redirect" title="Agathokleia">Agathokleia</a><br />(in <a href="/wiki/Gandhara" title="Gandhara">Gandhara</a>, <a href="/wiki/Punjab_(Pakistan)" class="mw-redirect" title="Punjab (Pakistan)">Punjab</a>)</div>
</td></tr>
